    "body":  "Transform current \"Quick Actions\" cards into interactive action buttons. These should serve as immediate launch points based on user role and scope.\n\n**Initial Actions (static for now):**\n\n1. Upload CV – Upload resume for parsing (open modal)\n2. Add Qualification – Manual entry of new qualification (launch form)\n3. Assign Role – Select user and assign job (modal, dummy for now)\n4. Run Compliance Check – Show simulated compliance panel\n\n- UI: 2x2 card layout\n- Behavior: Buttons should visually suggest interactivity\n- Implementation: Use static placeholders; future enhancements will enable dynamic behavior based on role\n\nNote: These are no longer navigation shortcuts. Each card should trigger an interactive action (e.g., open modal or launch panel). Please remove any href-based navigation if already implemented.",
